# Frechy - French Grammar Practice CLI
## Specification v1

## Overview
Minimal CLI interactive app to train French grammar using LLM-generated exercises. Initial focus on pronoun word order (e.g., "je lui ai dit" vs "j'ai lui dit"). Designed to be extensible to other grammar topics (articles, subjunctive, etc.). Tracks user sessions and progress in SQLite.

## Goals
- Practice specific French grammar topics with targeted exercises
- Two practice modes: translation and word-order
- LLM-generated exercises on-demand (via OpenRouter)
- Session tracking with topic-based progression
- Modular, extensible codebase for future topics
- Minimal, tight code for experimentation

## Non-Goals (Future Work)
- Free-form text input with grammar detection
- Adaptive difficulty based on performance within session
- Multi-user support beyond hardcoded username
- Web interface
- Spaced repetition scheduling

